parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause engine damage, leading to costly repairs, and potentially resulting in engine failure, which can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Motor Mount and Transmission Mount Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the motor mount and transmission mount can cause excessive vibration, leading to premature wear on other engine and transmission components, and potentially resulting in engine or transmission failure, which can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Excessive vibration when accelerating or decelerating
loud clunking or banging noises from the engine or transmission

a strong smell of exhaust fumes inside the vehicle

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Leaking master cylinder hydroboost units can cause a loss of brake fluid, leading to reduced braking performance, increased stopping distances, and potentially cause accidents.
